Package: ndopred
Title: Automated IUCN Red List Assessment for NDOP Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Jonáš", "Gaigr", , "jonas.gaigr@aopk.gov.cz", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Automates the calculation of IUCN Red List metrics using occurrence 
    data from the NDOP database. It includes functions to calculate Extent of 
    Occurrence (EOO), Area of Occupancy (AOO), population trends (Criterion A), 
    and population size metrics (Criteria C/D). The package implements strict 
    IUCN guidelines, including logic for Near Threatened (NT), Data Deficient (DD), 
    and Regionally Extinct (RE) statuses. Includes an interactive Shiny dashboard 
    for expert verification and manual overrides.
